			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1. Start the lakeside fight in Lifting the Curse. &#xD;&#xA;2. Wait for Halsin to emerge after a certain amount of turns.&#xD;&#xA;3. Or kill all enemies (killcombat breaks the situation)&#xD;&#xA;4. Dialog should start" />
